title: United Kingdom Imports Intra Eu - Wool, Fine & Coarse Animal Hair
description: Imports Intra Eu - Wool, Fine & Coarse Animal Hair in the United Kingdom increased to 10.84 GBP Million in September from 9.60 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports Intra Eu - Wool, Fine & Coarse Animal Hair in the United Kingdom averaged 12.86 GBP Million from 1996 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 31.23 GBP Million in March of 2019 and a record low of 4.16 GBP Million in April of 2020. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Intra EU - Wool, Fine & Coarse Animal.
